text: Þis his þæs wudes landgemære þe Aþelred cyning bocað Leofrice his þegene on ece yrfe.
Ærest of clæg broce on þa ealdan stræt be westan dunninc wicon andlang stræt on norþewerde wileardes hyrste on þone feld<../images/tbar.gif>on þætte <riþi> andlang Riþiges on Aþelnodes gemære.
<../images/tbar.gif>on þone rodweg andlang weges þe eft on clægbroc.
